00:03:22.760 --> 00:03:25.630
<i>Gen-san? Ve donanma?</i>  

00:03:32.010 --> 00:03:35.000
<i>Sen hırsız kız Nami misin?</i>

00:03:36.610 --> 00:03:42.350
