--Olamaz! Yani...  

00:10:09.600 --> 00:10:12.240
O alçak!  
Nacchan'ımıza yalan söylemiş!  

00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:13.730
Nacchan!  

00:10:17.580 --> 00:10:18.850
Nami...  

00:10:18.850 --> 00:10:23.340
